==German==
==={{initialism}}===
'''VPG'''
# ''Vielseitigkeitsprüfung für Gebrauchshunde''. Eng. ''Versatility examination for working dogs''. The name and abbreviation for working dog titles awarded by dog organizations other than the [[Wikipedia:Der Verein für Deutsche Schäferhunde|SV]] and other [[Wikipedia:German Shepherd Dog|German Shepherd Dog]] organizations. Equivalent to [[SchH]]. See also [[IPO]].